What follows here is not merely a fiction. It is a reflection of a sickness inherent in our world. An LD,,50,, of a toxin which pulses through veins of society, self-inflicted. While Lillian Marley has only began today's shift, she will find that she is to be scheduled overtime. To toil thanklessly, evermore, in the Borderless Confines.


